data.description: You will love this, feels like new, 5-bedroom, 5-bathroom open layout with walls of windows overlooking a private backyard adjacent to a wooded conservation area. You will be greeted with a soaring entry and grand staircase leading you up to a master suite and three additional bedrooms. The upstairs bedrooms offer 2 ensuite baths and one jack & jill. Enjoy a sitting area in the luxurious master suite with separate his & her custom closets. The basement has an additional bedroom and bathroom, the rest is unfinished and ready for you to custom design into your dream space! Your family will love the in-ground trampoline in the backyard and the neighborhood pool & park. The finished garage offers more entertainment space. Come see your next home!
